task.summary: Default task
Changed the reaction rate warning to apply to the species container, before iterating over all reactions.
Added function for irreversible reactions to check whether their rate contains their species.
Added function for reversible reactions to check whether their forward rate contains their species.
Added function for reversible reactions to check whether their reverse rate contains their species.
Changed species finding functions to use species nodes as arguments, as opposed to species expressions.
Checking rule for species in reaction rates now checks for specific species and reports them.
Investigating getting the relation intention to occur manually. Switching to testing prep.
Created test solution.
Added test for flat cell numbers.
Added test for total cell number in the tissue container. Also added parameter expressions as something that can be used by the species language.
Changed test to look over cell, vessel and monolayer in the container
Manually set world size in test.
Manually set world size in test.
Added function to get all parameter functions within an expression.
Added function to get all parameter functions within an expression.
Changed parameter and species expression functions to return a list of generic expression nodes and amended usages of these functions to reflect that fact.
Changed textgen for reactions to return the name of the reaction.
Added function to filter expression lists for unique species and parameters when constructing arguments.
Added species/parameter filter to species expression textgen
Added test to check that cell boundary locations are correct.
Set virtual packages for species, reactions and parameters
Implemented relations management for parameters

Tested parameter relations management. Added checks for cyclical references and self-references. Fixed generator for cell types to use height and width functions. Fixed cylindrical tissue generator to correctly define cells along circumference. Currently debugging grid calculation.
Added workaround for world not finding grid behaviours.
Added tissue container functions to get the grid's negative space value.
Updated cell position generation to factor in negative grid space.
Removed extraneous newline from tissue generator
Changed world.cpp generator to take into account negative grid space when placing objects.
World generator now uses concentration values of original species.
Added checks to ensure that names in the species container are unique.
Updated parameter and species getters to correctly return objects when the expression has no children. Also added asserts for when the expression is null.
Adding new modifiers to species setup languange.
Fixed graphical diagram to account for modifiers.
Added rates to reactions graphical editors.
Added arrows to denote reversible reactions.
Split Species container textgen into multiple sub components.
Implemented new modifier relations.
Moved all updating functions to a single intention.
Added test to check the boundaries of a blood vessel.
Added functions for determining the height and width of rectangular cells.
Changed generator to use new rectangular dimension functions
Generator uses correct cylinder radius function
Added semi-colons to generated gradient functions.
Removed gradient shape enum from generated create_gradient calls
Swapped generator arguments around to match declaration in source files.
Changed Y-vertex getter to return the correct value (was returning X-value).
Added two tests to check vessel properties are correct.
Added tests to check object overlap.
Commit before splitting of species textgen into header and source files.
